1)Ti tha exi i dilotiki query languange
  1)query se facts (giati einai pio fisiko na ekfrazis tis queries san facts)
  2)processing mono otan auto periorizo ton pinaka
    diladi anti na paro olo ton pinaka kai na to kano meta

    diladi processing pou kano kata tin diarkeia kataskeueis tou pinaka

    genika opou dilotikos tropos => oxi kataskeui oloklirou pinaka => to kano dilotika

    px  Group by , count

    mporo na paro ton pinaka kai na to kano,alla den iparxi logos,giati me niazi mono to count
    opote anti na paro ton pinaka olokliro,perno exarxis mono tis plirofories pou xriazome


